अक्षीण-माङ्गल्य-शत:	(and) undiminished in numerous auspiciousness
व्रज:-अयम्	Gokul this
भवत्-निवासात्-	by Thy living there
अयि वासुदेव	O Vaasudeva!
प्रमोद-सान्द्र:	full of happiness
परित: विरेजे	every where shone
O Vaasudeva! Day by day this Gokul developed with prosperity and undiminished auspiciousness as a result of Thy living there. Happiness and undecaying virtue shone everywhere.

